# Clerk Setup Instructions
# 1. Create a Clerk application at https://dashboard.clerk.dev
# 2. Copy your Publishable Key from the Clerk dashboard (should start with pk_test_ or pk_live_)
# 3. Configure your application URLs in the Clerk dashboard:
#    - Home URL: https://applymate.app
#    - Sign In URL: /sign-in
#    - Sign Up URL: /sign-up
#    - After Sign In URL: /jobs
#    - After Sign Up URL: /jobs
# 4. Configure OAuth providers (e.g., LinkedIn) in the Clerk dashboard
# 5. Add your domain to the allowed origins in the Clerk dashboard
